---
description: react-zmage repository rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` before editing. Keep changes scoped to the requested behavior, preserve the public API contract, and verify with the relevant `pnpm` scripts.

Treat `react-zmage` as a client-side React component package. Do not invent hosted API, OAuth, API key, webhook, MCP, account, or server-side image-processing behavior.
